THEN ETIENNE SQUEALS]

18:14.136 --> 18:19.141
- Mademoiselle Barbie, you startled me.
-I'm sorry.

18:19.308 --> 18:21.560
I was enjoying your singing.

18:21.727 --> 18:24.188
-So was Reynaud.
-Oh, heh.

18:24.354 --> 18:27.941
It is nothing. It calms him down.

18:28.150 --> 18:31.445
Monsieur Etienne, may I ask you a question...

18:31.653 --> 18:33.530
...about the Academy logo.

18:33.697 --> 18:35.032
LOQQ?

18:35.240 --> 18:38.243
-You know, the sign in front, the horse.
-Ah.

18:38.452 --> 18:42.122
That. Heh. Well, what can I say?
It is a horse.

18:42.331 --> 18:43.457
Well, yes, of course.

18:43.624 --> 18:46.710
But a very unusual horse, wouldn't you say'?

18:46.919 --> 18:50.839
-I mean, those markings.
-Why the interest?

18:51.048 --> 18:52.800
It's just.... I don't know...

18:52.966 --> 18:56.220
...I feel like I've seen that horse somewhere.

18:56.386 --> 18:58.514
