42:50.069 --> 42:51.779
Skateboards, mountain bikes...

42:51.987 --> 42:55.407
...wakeboarding, sky surfing, motor cross.

42:55.616 --> 42:58.118
So why can't I control a horse?

42:58.327 --> 43:01.330
