43:08.754 --> 43:14.093
Well, maybe you should try to work with her
instead of just trying to control her.

43:14.301 --> 43:16.637
Make friends. Find out what she wants.

43:16.845 --> 43:21.100
Make friends with a horse?
Like what, take her to a movie?

43:21.308 --> 43:24.103
-You know what I mean. Just try it.
-Ha-ha-ha!

43:25.312 --> 43:29.566
Oh, and these sugar cubes won't hurt.

43:30.526 --> 43:32.111
<i>Hmm.</i>

43:33.279 --> 43:35.906
Hi, I'm Stacie.

43:36.115 --> 43:38.284
You know, the girl you've been trying to maim.

43:39.159 --> 43:40.786
[GRUNTING]

43:41.328 --> 43:44.498
Here, have some cavities.

43:57.720 --> 44:00.723
