[ALL SIGH]

54:05.201 --> 54:09.539
She's okay. Just a little shaken. She'll be fine.

54:09.748 --> 54:13.710
- Chelsea, why on Earth--?
-I just wanted to ride a big horse...

54:13.919 --> 54:18.298
...like you and Barbie and Stacie do.

54:18.506 --> 54:23.637
Oh, Chelsea, I think you've done
quite enough riding for one day.

54:23.845 --> 54:25.472
Let's get you inside.

54:25.639 --> 54:29.851
