55:15.480 --> 55:17.983
Come on. This way.

55:22.237 --> 55:24.614
JONAS: Hmm.
BARBIE: What is it?

55:24.781 --> 55:26.741
JONAS:
These tracks.

55:28.785 --> 55:30.036
You see that set of prints?

55:30.245 --> 55:33.206
