56:42.108 --> 56:43.985
That horse...

56:44.194 --> 56:46.863
...the one with the pink mane.

56:48.531 --> 56:51.618
-What breed is it?
-A very special one.

56:51.826 --> 56:54.704
And they're our secret. Okay?

56:54.913 --> 56:57.457
Looks like the steeplechase is still on.

56:58.333 --> 57:00.335
[NEIGHING]

57:06.216 --> 57:07.550
[NEIGHING]

57:07.717 --> 57:11.346
Monsieur Philippe. What a pleasant surprise.

57:11.513 --> 57:16.017
