Yaah! Whoo-hoo!

01:04:43.839 --> 01:04:46.259
[ANNOUNCER TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

01:04:48.886 --> 01:04:50.471
[NEIGHS]

01:04:50.888 --> 01:04:52.431
[SCREAMS]

01:04:56.561 --> 01:05:02.650
ANNOUNCER: And the winner for Alpine Academy
is Barbie Roberts on Majesty!

01:05:02.817 --> 01:05:03.859
[NEIGHING]

01:05:06.571 --> 01:05:08.531
[COUGHS]

01:05:08.698 --> 01:05:11.200
[NEIGHING]

01:05:11.993 --> 01:05:13.494
[LAUGHS THEN PANTS]

01:05:13.661 --> 01:05:16.205
