01:05:36.267 --> 01:05:38.561
I was unfairly distracted.

01:05:38.728 --> 01:05:41.314
Hmm. By what? Your own cheating?

01:05:41.522 --> 01:05:44.442
We saw what you did, you penguin's patoot.

01:05:44.650 --> 01:05:47.945
And you are the lint in a baboon's belly button.

01:05:48.112 --> 01:05:50.114
Ah. Here we go again.

01:05:50.281 --> 01:05:51.699
[WOMAN SPEAKS IN FRENCH]

01:05:51.866 --> 01:05:53.242
