01:06:00.791 --> 01:06:02.209
[LAUGHING]

01:06:08.174 --> 01:06:10.760
<i>You were magnifique.</i>

01:06:12.345 --> 01:06:13.596
Thank you.

01:06:13.804 --> 01:06:18.100
Madame Cheynet,
the owner of Ecole Montagne.

01:06:18.309 --> 01:06:21.395
